{"tid":878293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港證監前CEO Martin Wheatley：中國經濟增長僅「虛構」股市崩潰將會更加嚴重","createTime":"2018-10-27T04:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T02:32:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1780f51d65b66560953b0877c7661c5e1242bba8","tid":878293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:19:20.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，香港證監會前行政總裁韋奕禮(Martin Wheatley)表示，中國的經濟增長僅屬「虛構」，相信<span style=\"color: red;\">中國股市崩潰將會更加嚴重</span>。<br />\n<br />\n韋奕禮稱，有很多原因必須遠離中國股票，直言投資者根本難以受惠於內地經濟增長，因為中國不完善的企業經營準則，令上市公司管理層很大程度上能根據自己的利益行事。<br />\n<br />\n中國國家統計局上周公布，第3季國內生產總值(GDP)增長按年放緩至6.5%，增速回落至近十年新低，並低於預期的增長6.6%。<br />\n<br />\n韋奕禮質疑指，中國14個主要地區都各自公布了經濟增速，但奇怪的是，這些地區經濟增長全都高於平均水平。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，內地中央政府此前的政策目標是8%的經濟增長，這個增速長期能夠維持只是「虛構的」，由政府操作去達成目標。然而，未來中美貿易戰升溫將打擊市場情緒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他對於中國前景感到擔憂，指內地工資低廉的優勢逐漸失去，就業需求在珠三角地區變得緊張，將推動工資上漲。<br />\n<br />\n同時，他相信，更多大型製造業公司將遷至印尼、菲律賓、孟加拉等地，因為這些地方過去10年一直維持低廉的工資。<br />\n<br />\n韋奕禮又警告，在金融危機時，中國政府推出3萬億元人民幣的刺激措施，已經流入基建項目、樓市和股市，然而，低成本的資金流動最終會終結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181027/bkn-20181027051224328-1027_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181027%2Fbkn-20181027051224328-1027_00842_001.html&d=J905N8VzsThzpFTMnrW4iGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=542dc3c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181027/bkn-20181027051224328-1027_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"be0bb3530f01966d7415f43415f230669e461999","tid":878293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831d24518ec8c77251dfeda3519c1a2f4986b654","tid":878293,"uid":141704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">熱</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5a3d365d56327d268965b3eb0ac494318424f92","tid":878293,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"支爆近了"},{"pid":"f0a12a2c3474000867acad13e644eef675b18422","tid":878293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e570eb58b103a3bc6ef02946279ff518366ca0","tid":878293,"uid":61280,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開始鬥快講返真話做好人鳥！！！！</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3d2df6528481d66bdd9ae31f8108420ecc0dc3","tid":878293,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49f24fd06701afb9ededa24c3c0c938180905edd","tid":878293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca6848de6b25d0769ab62bf3d1cd04669481ea7","tid":878293,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3d2df6528481d66bdd9ae31f8108420ecc0dc3","tid":878293,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T05:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" cl